es augmenting the skill points of your own samurai (strength, dexterity, endurance, magic) wearing the right combination of armor parts.<br><br>Combine the 4 basic skills to achieve the highest level of power that will make your attacks stronger and your defence the most resilient ever seen! Collect the cards (that will give you hints and information) when meeting enemies, taking power-ups, building weapons, armors and moving forward within the story.",
